.TH "JS_OF_OCAML-BUILD-FS" 1 "" "Js_of_ocaml 5.2.0+git-v1.5.8-2-gbedae99-dirty" "Js_of_ocaml Manual"
.\" Disable hyphenation and ragged-right
.nh
.ad l
.SH NAME
.P
js_of_ocaml\N'45'build\N'45'fs \N'45' Js_of_ocaml pseudo filesystem utility
.SH SYNOPSIS
.P
\fBjs_of_ocaml build\N'45'fs\fR [\fB\N'45'I\fR \fIDIR\fR] \fB\N'45'o\fR \fIFILE\fR [\fIOPTION\fR]… [\fIFILES\fR]…
.SH DESCRIPTION
.P
jsoo_fs is a tool for embeding files in a Js_of_ocaml pseudo filesystem\N'46'
.SH ARGUMENTS
.TP 4
\fIFILES\fR
Embed [\fIFILES\fR] in the js_of_ocaml pseudo filesystem\N'46'
.SH OPTIONS
.TP 4
\fB\N'45'I\fR \fIDIR\fR
Add [\fIDIR\fR] to the list of include directories\N'46'
.TP 4
\fB\N'45'o\fR \fIFILE\fR (required)
Set output file name to [\fIFILE\fR]\N'46'
.SH COMMON OPTIONS
.TP 4
\fB\N'45'\N'45'help\fR[=\fIFMT\fR] (default=\fBauto\fR)
Show this help in format \fIFMT\fR\N'46' The value \fIFMT\fR must be one of \fBauto\fR, \fBpager\fR, \fBgroff\fR or \fBplain\fR\N'46' With \fBauto\fR, the format is \fBpager\fR or \fBplain\fR whenever the \fBTERM\fR env var is \fBdumb\fR or undefined\N'46'
.TP 4
\fB\N'45'\N'45'version\fR
Show version information\N'46'
.SH EXIT STATUS
.P
\fBjs_of_ocaml build\N'45'fs\fR exits with:
.TP 4
0
on success\N'46'
.TP 4
123
on indiscriminate errors reported on standard error\N'46'
.TP 4
124
on command line parsing errors\N'46'
.TP 4
125
on unexpected internal errors (bugs)\N'46'
.SH BUGS
.P
Bugs are tracked on github at \fIhttps://github\N'46'com/ocsigen/js_of_ocaml/issues\fR\N'46'
.SH SEE ALSO
.P
ocaml(1)
.P
